# [Interview #974: AMOL Signing Report - J. Dauro, Entry #34](https://www.theoryland.com/intvmain.php?i=974#34)

#### Question

The chick (unintelligible) . . .

#### Brandon Sanderson

She is Nakomi, and it is left to your imagination and wondering who she might be.
